Interface ViewTransitionProvider<K,T>

    public interface ViewTransitionProvider<K,T>
extends ViewTransitionFactory<K,T>, TransitionProvider<K,T>
    A Transition Provider that can use the generic view_target pages. These show a html summary of the object and give buttons to invoke the possible transitions on the target.
